1.10	Forgent	Asure Software	Asure Software is a software company which has licensing as its primary revenue source. Prior to September 13, 2007, the company was known as Forgent Networks. Critics claim Asure profits primarily as a patent troll. It also has a software division, NetSimplicity, which specializes in room scheduling and fixed assets management software.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/f/f3/Forgent.png
